                     <interp inst="t18310908-228-person1702" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Police-officer. I took the prisoner with this coat on; he owned his own coat directly - I found in the pocket a begging letter, in his own name, and a quantity of broken victuals.</p>
